{
  "id": "adv_card_mna_06_01",
  "title": "長瀬麻奈 1話 うち、来る？",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-00-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-05.m4a",
      "text": "私、まだ結婚するつもりなんてないからね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not planning to get married yet!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "だいたい、誰からのプロポーズなの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "First of all‚ who even proposed to me!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.6666667699,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈……。誤解だ\n頼むから、俺の話を聞いてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana… It’s a misunderstanding.\nPlease‚ just listen to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.2999998807,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-09.m4a",
      "text": "嫌！　{user}くんの話なんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No! I don’t want to hear anything",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.8999782324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "聞きたくない！　結婚だってしないんだから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "from you! I’m not getting married anyway!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.6333128373,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "分かった、分かったから、頼む……！\n俺の説明が悪かった！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ I was wrong‚ please…!\nI didn’t explain it well!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.6666692178,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "結婚じゃなくて、麻奈を広告塔にしたウエディング企画\nなんだ。インタビューやCM、グラビア撮影の仕事だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not marriage‚ it’s a wedding project with you as the advertising model.\nIt’s a job for an interview‚ commercial‚ and gravure photoshoot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.5000025511,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_ask-04.m4a",
      "text": "へ？　……仕事？　ウエディング、の？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? …A job? A wedding…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.4560802063,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_emb-04.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、へぇ……そう、なんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… I see… So‚ that’s what it is?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.0227446476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_emb-02.m4a",
      "text": "紛らわしい言い方するから勘違いしちゃった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You said it in a confusing way‚ that’s why I misunderstood.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.5227472542,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_sorry-01.m4a",
      "text": "ちゃんと聞かずに騒いじゃってごめんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sorry for making a fuss without listening properly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.756081695,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-11.m4a",
      "text": "でもさっきのは{user}くんが悪いよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But that was your fault!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.556085165,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "急に「ウエディングドレスを着ないか」なんて言うから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You suddenly asked me‚ “Would you wear a wedding dress?”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.6560844869,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_ask-12.m4a",
      "text": "……ん？　でも、ウエディングの仕事？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hm? But‚ a wedding-themed job?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.4560912684,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_ask-16.m4a",
      "text": "なんで？　私、まだ高校卒業したばっかりだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why me? I just graduated from high school.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.0560940659,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ウエディングの仕事なんて勤まるかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Will I be able to do a wedding-themed job?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.3627513434,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、少し前にバレンタインのCMに出ただろ？\nあれを先方が観て、ぜひ麻奈にお願いしたいって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ you were in a Valentine’s Day commercial a while ago‚ right?\nThey saw that‚ and said they wanted to ask you to do it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.0000124374,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_surp-06.m4a",
      "text": "えぇっ！？　あ、あのCM！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh!? T-that commercial!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.4920759434,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "まだ恥ずかしいんだな……。でもこうして次の仕事に\n繋がるくらい好評だった、っていうことだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re still embarrassed about it… But it means\nit was well-received enough to lead to your next job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.8000165063,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_emb-04.m4a",
      "text": "そっかー、そんなに求められちゃったら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see~‚ if they want me that much",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.7501317575,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-05.m4a",
      "text": "応えない訳にもいかないよね！　やる！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t refuse! I’ll do it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.3034645631,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "もう少し真剣に考えてくれ。インタビューもあるんだぞ\n第一、結婚についてちゃんと考えたこと、あるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Think about it a little more seriously. There’s also an interview.\nHave you ever thought about marriage carefully?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.1000109114,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_no-02.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、正直……まだ考えたことないなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… To be honest… I haven’t thought about it yet…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.5897627427,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さっきも言ったけど、この間まで高校生だったし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like I said earlier‚ I was a high school student until recently.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.6164315586,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-07.m4a",
      "text": "とはいえ、せっかくのオファーだし、全力でやるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That being said‚ it’s a good offer‚ so I’ll do my best.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.1897647771,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "撮影までにはイメージを固めてくる。任せて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll solidify my image before the shoot. Leave it to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.4430899622,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_letter-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10056.90851179999,
          "startTime": 135.499998474
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈がそこまで言うなら、この仕事、受けよう\nじゃあ、これを書いておいてくれ",
      "translations": {
