      },
      "startTime": 133.3333294943,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_ask-03.m4a",
      "text": "インタビューの事前アンケート？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A preliminary interview questionnaire?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.2225173544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "こんなに考えることがあるんだ、なんか凄いね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s so much to think about‚ it’s impressive.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.2666620889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_06_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃ、考えることは沢山あるだろ\n結婚は人生の一大イベントだし、節目でもあるんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course there’s a lot to think about.\nMarriage is a big life event and a turning point.",
